title: '55 cms size is with wheels! Added width gives good volume.'
body: This bag is bright and in your face. Not for business people but its a peppy and cool bag for young adults. Quality is good and it can easily carry 2-3 day's clothes. Width is quite big and so it packs a lot pf stuff in it. The zipper compartment on the front (main compartment) has no straps which is a minus. My daughter loved it. The colors are duller than suggested.. more like dark peach and not bright red! Remember total volume allowed is 115 cms total inside the airplane !! Do your math and buy accordingly.
